Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1 GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 好好擊掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果太慢 接力將沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你剛才沒有追上我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才在你前面減速的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種行為就叫作放水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再認真一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經足夠認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你從沒考慮過搭檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？說什麼相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是我的指示太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 櫻井同學沒有任何錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井 剛才那樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把時機縮短一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快到極限的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我沒有做好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天也差不多快黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再稍微跑一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學可真熱衷於練習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已經超過了喜歡的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什麼會拚命到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是巴一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看 仔細聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看準時機再下達指令
