Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成文規定？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像離四字成語還差一字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但反過來說 只要有贊助商願意贊助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一支隊伍也能有好幾個贊助商
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星學園什麼的真是賺翻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起西星 因為有很多隊員都是當紅藝人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也讓我們從將棋的世界裡聞名遠揚怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將棋對宣傳有幫助麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太low了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不下將棋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秒拒三人組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好犀利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有別的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有KGB的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KGB？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂KBG
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 久 我 暴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法·貓爪之地獄突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門…門脇學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個話題打住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉 現在已經是這種現狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來只有去拜託D's了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D's是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D's INTERNATIONAL（D's國際集團）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海格力斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JSTT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經營這些品牌服裝的就是D's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有個小錢包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是去拜託他們 就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是希斯姐姐經營的公司嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經營…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他姐姐是社長嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D's的D是指支倉代替方案的D哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是超邪惡的D
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你說走 你知道在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩 我們一起去拜託他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想多扯上關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉 雖說我尊重你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請當機立斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.92,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,*當機立斷 當場立即做出決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來只能捨卒保車了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當即決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有顧問會在連贊助商都沒有的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就申請參加比賽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊助商合同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是壇老師的簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗中搗鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我是有條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲得月末的春季疾走節的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D's可是勝者的品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也當即決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然你們也要去做模特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你絕對會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼盡快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就有新作的試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣告就拜託你們拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又當即決定
