Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反間苦肉計
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收起反光傘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和穿運動服相反 看上去很棒麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原 超級帥的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如果不願意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 做了也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願意做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學 我呢我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神也很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 今天要你們換很多套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的孩子也快點過來換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長親自擔任造型師 太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就是個獨裁者罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是自己想幹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至連自己的貼身保鏢也是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.10,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,希斯 眼神朝這兒看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 支倉前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去就像真的模特一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩是什麼都行的類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他小時候就被迫要求做模特了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提 這是希斯作為模特出道時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好萌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿給別人看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持著模特式微笑生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張大概是2年前拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了別給他們看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔哇 這張也很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 旁邊一起入鏡的人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你是八神的弟弟嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在正在美國留學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留學?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴已經不在方南學園了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子也是個很好的模特兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也有在玩疾走嗎 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豈止是有在疾走而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是高中最強的疾走跑者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 有一起練習疾走嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我中學時放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進了中學之後 發現其他運動也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打球 接球 跳起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有八神同學的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 難得都重新開始參加疾走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能跟哥哥一起練習就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不夠認真面對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跑一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑一下…現在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連八神同學也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群奇怪的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這地步了 你還不死心阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是有女孩子在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的女孩子阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事不是都要來真的才好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你太野蠻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野蠻又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 男孩子的小日向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 總是找我麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憐治大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝你 靜馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬力全開 結果卻撞牆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游馬  你說得太過分了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒學過「轉彎處潛藏著危險」這句話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有「在狹小的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼急急忙忙的是打算去那兒呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你也好好道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星學園的黛靜馬和黛游馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 諏訪憐治
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜馬 這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶的吉祥物 神戶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜馬真是什麼都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為憐治大人什麼事都會問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人那會知道這些亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要神戶太郎的吊飾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們下周在神戶有現場演唱會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的三角飛 稍微讓我心動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊 那群閃亮亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管對手是誰  我們都會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那種閃亮的程度我們比不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小日向學長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這不是很不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就取名為…「天使的初戀」怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初戀天使殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拿出勇氣面對全新的自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑也能找到勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  眼鏡君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步 你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你培養了我這個世界最快將棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要很就恨你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種閃耀的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有小日向學長在的話 我們也贏得過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是真正的笨蛋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑過頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是比有沒有超過接棒區更基本的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門脇  速度再加快一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙和別人的協調性是零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 就拜託你們鎖門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要穿體育服回去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經要回去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再看一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這是 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的接力成功率 只有藤原同學特別低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那傢伙 完全不顧對方地在跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學所花費的平均時間 是最短的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不管是他交接 還是交接給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學一直在配合對方的最快速度進行接力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我以後也想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信著藤原同學的速度來指揮比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在跑者看來 可能是件很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意地相信對方去交接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是疾走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你在等風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感知到風 就會毫不猶豫地站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後飛奔而出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來 風將會推動你的後背
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 無懈可擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來練習接力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你休息好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1 Go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學一直在配合對方的最快速度進行接力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我以後也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信著藤原同學的速度來指揮比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續保持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全速奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是藤原同學所期待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神同學的速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可難輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的配合 就和棒銀的效果一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:31.99,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,*棒銀：將棋用語 進攻方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是最低標準
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還可以更快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 那必須
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的比賽 要跑出更快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽的對手換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 都這個時候才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運營委員那邊出了點狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們初賽的對手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星學園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上來就和東日本最強等級交手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星就是…那個時候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管對手是誰 我們都要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣 原來的… 是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊 輸了的話又要重新找贊助了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也讓心頭吹上一陣舒適的風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉祥寺春季疾跑賽
