Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 又輸給藤原了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小陸 你永遠也贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊和希斯是歡呼聲不斷的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡稱K2G
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 疾走王子 「M2G的逆襲」　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 M2G難道是完全不受歡迎的意思
